{"lemma":"خُصْيَةٍ","slug":"خُصْيَةٍ","root":"خ.ص.#","root_slug":"خ-ص-_","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ص-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10831","n10832"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D8%B5%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the testicle","tags":["countable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xusˤ.ja/","/xasˤ.ja/","/xisˤ.ja/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10831","headword_ar":"خُصْيَةٌ","root":"xSY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A testicle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Umawee, S;) sing. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSFY","text_ar":"خُصًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Mgh, Msb, K;) it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the organs of generation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSoyapN","text_ar":"خِصْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (S, K,) and so does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoYN","text_ar":"خُصْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSoYN","text_ar":"خِصْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSowapN","text_ar":"خُصْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var., occurring in a trad., but is extr.: (Sh, TA:) accord. to some, (Msb,) the sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoyapN","text_ar":"خُصْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[alone], (T, Msb,) of the fem. gender; (T, TA;) and the dual is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoyaAni","text_ar":"خُصْيَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ElUmawee, T, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) of the masc. gender, (T, TA,) without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":", (El-Umawee, S, Mgh, Msb,) irreg., (El-Umawee, S, Msb,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloyaAni","text_ar":"اَلْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"dual of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloyapN","text_ar":"اَلْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (El-Umawee, S,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoyataAni","text_ar":"خُصْيَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (T, Mgh, K,) this latter being sometimes used, (T, Mgh,) though rarely, (MF on the authority of the Expositions of the Fs,) both mentioned by ISh: (T, TA:) AO says, I have heard"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoyap","text_ar":"خُصْيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, but I have not heard ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSoyap","text_ar":"خِصْيَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr; and I have heard ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoyaAhu","text_ar":"خُصْيَاهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as the dual], though they did not use ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSoYN","text_ar":"خُصْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the sing.; (S;) IB, however, cites exs. of this last as a sing.: (TA:) AA says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuSoyataAni","text_ar":"الخُصْيَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two testicles;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AaxuSoyaAni","text_ar":"اَخُصْيَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two skins"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which compose the scrotum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which are the two testicles;"},{"kind":"text","text":"citing an ex. in which the latter dual is used in this sense; (S;) and ISk says the like; whereas IKoot makes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuSoyapu","text_ar":"الخُصْيَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to signify ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the scrotum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the skin containing the testicle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An earring"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quroTN","text_ar":"قُرْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the ear:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, Sgh, K:) thus called by way of comparison: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuSFY","text_ar":"خُصًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (JK.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","Sh","TA","T","Mgh","JK","Sgh"]},{"entry_id":"n10832","headword_ar":"خِصْيَةٌ","root":"xSY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}